Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}SAI終端服務一般被稱為回收方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在世界各地共有29個部門
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我所就職的第一終端服務 負責管轄總部所在的遠東地區
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這之後又要去總部開會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胃又痛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉可以幫我泡杯茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}課長 別老是把艾拉當作泡茶的使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在她可是司的執行者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請在這裡簽字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只不過是還沒改掉習慣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唷 諸位好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}縹康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們的觀測者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別看那樣 他可是在這裡工作快十年的老手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這小子 放著工作不做去哪裡偷懶了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然是帶薪休假或者出差什麼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來去女人那裡叫做出差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還是第一次這樣聽說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}記住這個絕不會吃虧的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.49,0:01:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝君那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真棒 艾拉你泡的茶依然是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是那個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和艾拉組隊的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我叫水柿司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是那個啥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和伍堂部長打招呼 照顧進來的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我說你啊 和部長是什麼樣的關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請一定要告訴我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為得了闌尾炎結果應試失敗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有必要就不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感謝你的父親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這次是特例
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 如果我認為你並不適合在我們公司工作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會立刻開除你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}記住了嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}部長和我父親認識
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和你有點話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉～ 我的搭檔呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂 再多來點笑容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們這裡的女孩子 為什麼表情都這麼可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是因為你這幾天丟下工作不管的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}關於這個 還希望你可以充分的說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉呀 但是我肚子有點餓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想先去吃點東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個笑話可真是好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要太緊張 放鬆點好好幹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}救命啊…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是柳豐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們並不是可疑的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老實地將那邊的馬克思交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們是終端服務 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}你們搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}馬克思快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂等等 為什麼要嚇唬他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤 我沒有聽清楚 請再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之先追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待著別動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被他們跑掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看來又要寫檢討了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們先回去了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這都第幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三次…了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已經安排相當輕鬆的工作給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果三次都被拒簽同意書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果有好好和艾拉建立了信賴關係的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該不會變成這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}畢竟是走後門的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不費一絲辛勞就進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 下次我會注意的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惡 司那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能確實說的太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿總是直言不諱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說完又開始後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔 你和司吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才沒有那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘴上說著討厭討厭 其實很喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}清清純純的很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥 我和司才不是這種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都說了不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得和平時沒什麼兩樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天下班後有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有空的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你有在喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一開始就說我還未成年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說 你和艾拉有好好相處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「不知道她在想什麼」之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能告訴我關於艾拉的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月以前和艾拉是搭檔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我告訴你也沒有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果本人不去互相理解也是白費
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也覺得很過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把她交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們這麼多的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概也是因為艾拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然艾拉是那樣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可要好好和她相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜託你這種事我也是醉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 我想和艾拉進一步搞好關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這傢伙是蘿莉控嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老闆再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}課長和總部總說要提高什麼工作效率
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}根本就是胡來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也做了將近十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到現在也看不到正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}誰知道到底該如何銷毀回憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}誰都不會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如何銷毀回憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有在聽嗎 新人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香 香月小姐 好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}耶 香月喝多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝先生怎麼也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是這裡的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這傢伙喝了多少杯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有三杯左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道說她酒量很差？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之我先送她回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經是常事了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 關門就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊 那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您辛苦了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H000000&\fs30\bord0\1a&H80&\frz7.458\pos(674,261)\frx344\fry10}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H000000&\fs28\bord0\1a&H80&\frz7.458\pos(584,457)\frx348\fry10}\h\h\h\h\h\h單元測驗房\N[訓練]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}單元測驗房？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是哪裡
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 總部大樓裡竟然還有這種設施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是艾拉的觀測者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們是終端服務部的專屬工程師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是繪瑠 這位是鐵黑右次郎師父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請跪拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無視我嗎 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在採集數據
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}數據？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是在測量身體能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}討厭 居然偷看少女的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是個糟糕的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她經常會來做這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是 只是和小司搭檔之後才經常來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為最近負擔也變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}保養的次數也增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我倒希望她能休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}負擔？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身體的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為以前就只是倒倒茶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而現在回到現場工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}情況當然是不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別光動嘴不動手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 對不起 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過看起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有點慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}擅自跑過來看 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼 我也沒有躲藏著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼突然要訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是在介意工作上的失誤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}時隔許久回到現場工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身體沒能像想像中那樣行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在的我在拖司的後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是因為空檔期的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很快就會找回感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 不只是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和持有者溝通的時候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像立刻就會變得很僵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暖…因為沒有做暖機運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 暖機運轉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又不是以前的汽車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的需要嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定要解決
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作為你的執行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能再給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果司已經覺得受不了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就只能解散我們的搭檔關係了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我這人呢 其實很墨守成規的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}工作的話守規矩還是很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以來這以後 我還是儘量試著讀懂規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是相當的應付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「臨機應變地對應」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「用最好的方法應對」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}具體的內容一點都沒寫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我能做的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}按照規則上寫的隨機應變地對應而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}隨機應變？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比如說 和持有者之間的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不讓艾拉來做 而讓我來做怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是觀測者的工作是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}監督搭檔的執行者 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然我知道這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但好不容易能成為搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}互相幫助一下也挺好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在艾拉找回感覺之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依靠一下我這種人也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不要這樣試一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣決定的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就盡力來制定自己的規則吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…去下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很好！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 我下次會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊 滿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 你覺得司這人怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才…才沒有什麼奇怪的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和小司搭檔是不是成為你的負擔了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我感覺你最近很明顯地在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不必對司這樣的新人太客氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不願意的話就說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你只是被課長強行和他組隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且…拖後腿的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那傢伙真是 果然是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗚嘎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然不向我如實彙報
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「不找藉口才帥氣」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你難道是這樣想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我說過那麼多次 不要再把自己當學生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿 不要太生司的氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 首先是傾聽對方的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是附和對方就能讓人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊 在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司在問我一些奇怪的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和回收對象的持有者交涉時 都需要注意些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼說 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到底是無能還是蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這又怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提爾是有感情的 持有者也是有感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是從香月那裡現學現賣來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽著 僅僅回收吉芙提爾是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否則的話 我們的工作只能帶來悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要依順吉芙提爾和持有者雙方的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雙方都要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概只有我們這裡會這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就連本部也對這種方法避而不用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 因為我是贊成香月的想法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以既然你來這裡工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就要實踐這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了 謝謝你教給我這些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 塞克 要去工作了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 現在就去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天真的有那麼要緊的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有 司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次對你說了很多過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿一大早就這麼激動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是到了複雜的年紀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我懂的 我家的女兒也是完全不聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請別說那種令人悲傷的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 差不多就這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唷 真是努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉太會使喚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在做自己用的工作手冊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼 比起我 艾拉更努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}單元測驗房啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為了找回在空白期裡丟失的感覺 每天都在進行訓練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 不管能不能找回感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冒冒失失的樣子大概是不會變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個孩子真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明知是徒勞 卻還是這麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徒勞？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉就是那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底是什麼意思呢 徒勞什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…艾拉的身體測試數據
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微瞥到過一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是一直在下降？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對 不是因此才為了彌補空白期而進行訓練的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提爾和人類還有其他機器人一樣要學習
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 吉芙提爾並沒有空白期的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他們體內原本就沒有植入遺忘功能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以這到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎樣訓練都是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉以後一直會是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那孩子自己也應該明白才對
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是因為我太不可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才讓她那麼勉強自己的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝 我…會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都被她那樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}柳豐先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請聽我說完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們是SAI公司的終端服務人員
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是來通知您馬克思的回收時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回收？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次讓您受驚了 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要回收了啊 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次逃走了真是抱歉
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是司的報告書？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.42,0:23:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 他們兩個意外的很合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.76,0:23:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過還真是讓我吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.36,0:23:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你居然什麼都沒跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別裝了 你沒和他說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉所剩的壽命還有2000小時的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
